{"tid":2415123,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"獲安排下周一注射新冠疫苗　葉劉：十分期待","createTime":"2021-02-20T04:09:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T04:59:49.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e20f8490e4e9fae3be977b0191bfbac5303b031e","tid":2415123,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:09:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/432p0/0x0/100/hd/555c8d9669f6319364db7aeddb3c1802/stheadline/inewsmedia/20210220/_2021022008232536881.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F432p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F555c8d9669f6319364db7aeddb3c1802%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20210220%2F_2021022008232536881.jpg&h=4fd2b306&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首批一百萬劑科興新冠疫苗已經抵港，除了特首林鄭月娥及問責團隊，行政會議成員及立法會議員亦獲安排在下星期一，率先往銅鑼灣中央圖書館展覽廳接種疫苗，以身作則，藉此鼓勵市民及早接種疫苗。當中林鄭團隊會在下周一下午率先打針，跟住到行會成員，之後輪到立法會議員上陣。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員陳克勤表示，全球疫情厲害，對疫苗的渴求非常殷切，國家主席習近平早前亦提到對香港疫情非常憂慮，國家今次肯優先向香港提供一百萬劑疫苗，顯示國家很緊張香港。他作為立法會議員，可以身作則帶頭接種疫苗，覺得非常幸運，希望其他市民如果有機會都盡早去打針，因為當疫情停下來，香港經濟民生才有機會復甦，那些無謂猜疑、政治陰謀論，應該放埋一邊，抗疫優先。<br />\n<br />\n新民黨主席葉劉淑儀就以行會成員身分打針，她在社交網站話，得知科興疫苗已經抵港，馬上向行會秘書處查詢幾時可以接種疫苗，仲問埋已經率先接種國藥疫苗、兼任全國政協的林健鋒及劉業強等，引述他們指完全無副作用及不良反應。她每年打流感針都無問題，十分期待打第一針疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n經民聯梁美芬亦將接種疫苗，認為不但對自己好，有了抗體之後，又可保護身邊人，更能讓香港早日實現群體免疫，有條件放寬社交距離措施和出入境檢疫安排，重過正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n不過熱血公民鄭松泰就拒絕打針，直言對目前的疫苗無信心，況且既然一劑難求，他願意讓給高危人士率先接種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2003250/即時-港聞-林鄭月娥團隊下周一打科興疫苗-立會議員鄭松泰拒打\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2003250%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0%E6%8B%92%E6%89%93&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkptjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=39d4cbb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F2003250%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%9C%88%E5%A8%A5%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%80%E6%89%93%E7%A7%91%E8%88%88%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97-%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E9%84%AD%E6%9D%BE%E6%B3%B0%E6%8B%92%E6%89%93&h=0077dda3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/2003250/即時-港聞-林鄭月娥團隊下周一打科興疫苗-立會議員鄭松泰拒打</a>"},{"pid":"5579d98b652da1964a6c29bc29696b6cc8c33d97","tid":2415123,"uid":177916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"姐姐。。。下世努力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81fb184c28fd608283ed289f48e6ade7bd20ad9b","tid":2415123,"uid":280329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"期待有好消息"},{"pid":"f9e657b8dce209cca5fb9d6bfa6997650374e424","tid":2415123,"uid":343712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:32:35.000Z","msg":"要有第三方獨立會計師認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81125589d1a9f202258753d14bd6b02362909a9","tid":2415123,"uid":8776,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sEwDYsw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsEwDYsw.jpg&h=7febc8f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b76328463abc4ce2d26db0d7813b8dc66a59e2d","tid":2415123,"uid":125017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:36:05.000Z","msg":"國藥又唔係科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c824f19f584324dcbc94caed9b40f611aeb72656","tid":2415123,"uid":339053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c